## Avoid

❌ Don't use arbitrary values unless absolutely necessary (gradients and brand colors are exceptions)
❌ Don't introduce new color schemes outside the defined palette
❌ Avoid default Tailwind shadows (use corporate shadows: shadow-corporate, shadow-corporate-md, shadow-corporate-lg)
❌ Don't use bold text everywhere (reserve for emphasis, use font-bold on gradients, font-medium on standard backgrounds)
❌ Avoid inconsistent spacing (stick to 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32px scale)
❌ Don't mix px values with Tailwind classes (use Tailwind spacing classes)
❌ Avoid excessive animations (use duration-200 or duration-300 for most transitions)
❌ Don't use Tailwind classes for gradients (always use inline styles)
❌ Avoid mixing gradient directions inconsistently (use 135deg for diagonal, `to right` for horizontal)
❌ Don't use black text on gradient backgrounds (always use white)
❌ Avoid heavy borders everywhere (use border-2 or border-3 only for emphasis)
❌ Don't use rounded-full for cards or containers (use rounded-lg or rounded-xl)
❌ Avoid mixing border colors (use gray-200/300 for subtle, #2E5AAC for emphasis)

